### Climate Prediction API Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Test main page
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Test weather endpoint - London
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather/London

### Test weather endpoint - New York
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather/New York

### Test weather endpoint - Tokyo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather/Tokyo

### Test weather endpoint - Paris
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather/Paris

### Test weather endpoint - Sydney
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather/Sydney

### Test forecast endpoint - London
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/forecast/London

### Test forecast endpoint - Mumbai
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/forecast/Mumbai

### Test search history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history

### Test popular cities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/popular

### Test invalid city (should return error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather/InvalidCityName123

### Test empty city name (should return error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/weather/

### Test forecast for invalid city
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/forecast/InvalidCityName123